uid":224007,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"2012年8月，於無綫電視立法會九龍西選舉論壇上，蔣麗芸被黃毓民問到中華人民共和國國旗的5顆星代表甚麼，蔣麗芸回答稱：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「工、農、兵、商」</span></span>。黃毓民指正，四小星分別代表工人階級、農民階級、小資產階級及民族資產階級，黃毓民隨即又問蔣麗芸在1958年推行的「三面紅旗」是甚麼，蔣麗芸未能回應，黃毓民指，分別是人民公社、總路線及大躍進。 在場的公民黨毛孟靜揶揄蔣麗芸號稱「愛國」自居，卻連中共的基本歷史也懵然不知。<br />\n<br />\n愛國喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b751ad9525adeef9188b5633d7ec32881dd9a4","tid":1223011,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:02:53.000Z","msg":"佢算唔算女版terry?"},{"pid":"e2007515c8472884f88f3308391377e9f43a3f92","tid":1223011,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"奶共都係弱智的，唔明係啱的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030d8ce78d3879bf205e6d7df9f1a66d985fffaa","tid":1223011,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11557af754c7d9f822dd1a322121ae0109fec451","tid":1223011,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dec6c16f080c3008067030c13a9f54f81c4f50a9","tid":1223011,"uid":184827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"你老豆聽到都彈返起身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"蔣震未死架"},{"pid":"660f6fff8b0d8ec6170e2e0c76664ce05a4d03e3","tid":1223011,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"咁你班仆街美帝通過法案都唔好撚嘈<br />\n我同你講番依句"},{"pid":"ddac0a247bfbef638278eedb54b3c198475b5282","tid":1223011,